1
00:00:00,760 --> 00:00:03,560
♪Shrugging off past burdens♪

2
00:00:03,560 --> 00:00:06,150
♪Beneath the mask, who am I?♪

3
00:00:06,820 --> 00:00:10,220
♪Release and find wider shores♪

4
00:00:11,920 --> 00:00:14,930
♪Love's a riddle, and rain pours heavy♪

5
00:00:15,300 --> 00:00:17,830
♪Crossed paths, now downward fall♪

6
00:00:18,170 --> 00:00:21,610
♪From dust arises starlight's spark♪

7
00:00:23,360 --> 00:00:28,580
♪Tearing through
the night's dense blockade♪

8
00:00:29,260 --> 00:00:34,340
♪Heart's flame illuminates all solitude♪

9
00:00:35,140 --> 00:00:37,630
♪Let time's sails drift endlessly♪

10
00:00:37,630 --> 00:00:40,240
♪Through wandering exile♪

11
00:00:40,760 --> 00:00:48,020
♪Breaking free from the cocoon,
I start anew♪

12
00:00:48,990 --> 00:00:51,750
♪Moon as song, life as flame♪

13
00:00:51,810 --> 00:00:54,650
♪Nameless heart clings fiercely♪

14
00:00:54,940 --> 00:00:55,970
♪Let me♪

15
00:00:56,160 --> 00:01:00,240
♪Charge toward the next raging river♪

16
00:01:00,690 --> 00:01:03,370
♪Moon darts, snow falls♪

17
00:01:03,660 --> 00:01:06,360
♪We tread rugged paths to reunite♪

18
00:01:06,530 --> 00:01:08,000
♪Hands held tight♪

19
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:12,170
♪We forever live for love's sake♪

20
00:01:12,530 --> 00:01:22,780
♪Shadow's spear burns fiercely♪

21
00:01:24,210 --> 00:01:29,760
=Legend of The Female General=

22
00:01:29,960 --> 00:01:32,900
=Episode 6=

23
00:01:33,140 --> 00:01:34,300
Not He Yan?

24
00:01:34,500 --> 00:01:35,400
Wait, Mr. Shen.

25
00:01:35,400 --> 00:01:36,780
But He took first place.

26
00:01:37,020 --> 00:01:38,500
- He...
- First place, so what?

27
00:01:40,460 --> 00:01:41,340
Get back to it.

28
00:01:41,539 --> 00:01:42,380
Don't make a scene.

29
00:01:44,180 --> 00:01:45,259
Listen up, all of you.

30
00:01:45,259 --> 00:01:46,940
Commander selects the candidate

31
00:01:47,140 --> 00:01:49,060
based on a comprehensive evaluation.

32
00:01:50,100 --> 00:01:52,500
The competition was just one aspect.

33
00:02:07,660 --> 00:02:08,860
They've got poor judgment.

34
00:02:09,139 --> 00:02:09,979
Right.

35
00:02:09,979 --> 00:02:10,820
Come on.

36
00:02:11,300 --> 00:02:12,140
Let's drink.

37
00:02:12,140 --> 00:02:12,980
Let's drink.

38
00:02:13,540 --> 00:02:15,140
So eager to join the battalion?

39
00:02:19,140 --> 00:02:20,340
Only then

40
00:02:21,020 --> 00:02:22,340
can I earn merits in combats.

41
00:02:22,780 --> 00:02:24,420
Only then can I become a general.

42
00:02:25,820 --> 00:02:28,260
In such a hurry for glorious homecoming?

43
00:02:36,020 --> 00:02:37,100
I have no family.

44
00:02:40,620 --> 00:02:41,660
All I want

45
00:02:43,340 --> 00:02:44,740
is to prove my worth.

46
00:02:46,380 --> 00:02:47,220
Lei Hou

47
00:02:47,860 --> 00:02:49,260
is your defeated opponent.

48
00:02:49,900 --> 00:02:51,460
Huaijin chose him over you.

49
00:02:52,140 --> 00:02:53,180
That's his loss.

50
00:03:32,620 --> 00:03:33,620
Let's drink.

51
00:03:35,180 --> 00:03:36,020
Here.

52
00:03:38,700 --> 00:03:39,820
The Mid-Autumn Festival.

53
00:03:40,220 --> 00:03:41,140
Family reunion day.

54
00:03:41,940 --> 00:03:43,460
I'll drink my fill.

55
00:03:48,020 --> 00:03:48,860
Cheers.

56
00:03:50,700 --> 00:03:52,540
- Being happy, I won't get drunk.
- Eat a lot.

57
00:04:08,500 --> 00:04:09,340
Xiao Jue.

58
00:04:09,460 --> 00:04:10,500
You've gone too far!

59
00:04:11,620 --> 00:04:12,460
What did you call me?

60
00:04:17,380 --> 00:04:18,420
Xiao Jue.

61
00:04:21,940 --> 00:04:23,620
Are you stupid?

62
00:04:23,980 --> 00:04:26,500
You don't even know your name.

63
00:04:32,460 --> 00:04:33,300
Xiao Jue.

64
00:04:33,500 --> 00:04:34,860
Do you know who I am?

65
00:04:38,140 --> 00:04:38,980
Who are you?

66
00:04:47,140 --> 00:04:47,980
I

67
00:04:48,620 --> 00:04:49,860
have been walking around

68
00:04:49,860 --> 00:04:50,860
with only one name.

69
00:04:51,300 --> 00:04:52,140
That is

70
00:04:52,140 --> 00:04:52,980
He Yan.

71
00:04:52,980 --> 00:04:54,060
The top one

72
00:04:55,380 --> 00:04:56,220
of Yezhou Garrison.

73
00:05:09,620 --> 00:05:10,860
How much did you drink?

74
00:05:13,060 --> 00:05:14,700
Go sober up.

75
00:05:20,980 --> 00:05:21,820
Sober up.

76
00:05:24,260 --> 00:05:25,700
Go sober up.

77
00:05:35,500 --> 00:05:36,340
Wait.

78
00:05:37,460 --> 00:05:38,620
Why should I leave?

79
00:05:39,940 --> 00:05:41,100
You haven't told me

80
00:05:41,980 --> 00:05:45,060
why you didn't
let me join the battalion.

81
00:05:45,460 --> 00:05:46,300
I am

82
00:05:46,300 --> 00:05:47,900
the top one of Yezhou Garrison,

83
00:05:50,659 --> 00:05:52,820
an outstanding candidate.

84
00:05:54,060 --> 00:05:54,900
You

85
00:05:55,580 --> 00:05:57,060
have terrible judgment!

86
00:06:04,060 --> 00:06:06,860
I actually know
why you didn't select me.

87
00:06:07,340 --> 00:06:08,820
You suspect

88
00:06:09,420 --> 00:06:10,700
there's a spy.

89
00:06:15,380 --> 00:06:18,620
But you kept testing me repeatedly.

90
00:06:18,820 --> 00:06:20,740
You clearly know I'm not.

91
00:06:26,280 --> 00:06:27,300
Lei Hou.

92
00:06:31,380 --> 00:06:32,460
It's Lei Hou.

93
00:06:38,220 --> 00:06:39,060
See?

94
00:06:39,500 --> 00:06:40,580
Am I clever?

95
00:06:43,100 --> 00:06:44,340
You are clever indeed.

96
00:06:45,180 --> 00:06:46,060
But clever people

97
00:06:46,940 --> 00:06:48,380
often meet bad ends.

98
00:06:48,860 --> 00:06:50,420
What bad end?

99
00:06:51,380 --> 00:06:52,540
Let me tell you.

100
00:06:52,810 --> 00:06:54,659
I, He Yan,

101
00:06:54,900 --> 00:06:55,860
will one day

102
00:06:56,620 --> 00:06:58,460
become a celebrated general.

103
00:07:28,420 --> 00:07:29,260
He Yan.

104
00:07:45,060 --> 00:07:45,900
Put it back.

105
00:07:47,820 --> 00:07:48,740
He Yan, put it back.

106
00:07:49,180 --> 00:07:50,020
Commander.

107
00:07:50,220 --> 00:07:52,420
Don't be angry.

108
00:07:52,659 --> 00:07:55,420
I'll perform a sword dance for you.

109
00:08:53,620 --> 00:08:54,460
Know you're wrong?

110
00:09:02,420 --> 00:09:03,260
No need to kneel.

111
00:09:12,460 --> 00:09:13,460
Xiao Jue,

112
00:09:15,460 --> 00:09:17,060
do you like me?

113
00:09:22,660 --> 00:09:23,500
Feinu,

114
00:09:23,900 --> 00:09:24,740
this is...?

115
00:09:25,580 --> 00:09:27,860
I will bring dinner for the Commander.
What about you?

116
00:09:27,900 --> 00:09:29,940
The banquet is not over. Why come here?

117
00:09:30,380 --> 00:09:32,260
I've been selected for the battalion.

118
00:09:32,780 --> 00:09:34,140
I wanted to thank the Commander.

119
00:09:34,700 --> 00:09:36,180
But I never expected he...

120
00:09:44,060 --> 00:09:46,020
You must dislike me.

121
00:09:46,620 --> 00:09:47,460
Otherwise,

122
00:09:47,700 --> 00:09:50,820
why wouldn't you
let me join the battalion?

123
00:09:53,860 --> 00:09:54,700
Let go.

124
00:09:56,140 --> 00:09:57,140
This is outrageous.

125
00:09:57,220 --> 00:09:58,300
You have poor judgment.

126
00:09:58,300 --> 00:09:59,700
I'm so disappointed in you.

127
00:10:00,460 --> 00:10:01,300
Tell me.

128
00:10:02,260 --> 00:10:03,940
In terms of looks,

129
00:10:04,300 --> 00:10:05,140
martial skills,

130
00:10:05,620 --> 00:10:07,660
or height,

131
00:10:07,740 --> 00:10:08,620
where am I lacking?

132
00:10:10,620 --> 00:10:12,420
Tell me, where am I lacking?

133
00:10:14,420 --> 00:10:15,260
Height?

134
00:10:17,900 --> 00:10:19,220
Even considering

135
00:10:19,620 --> 00:10:21,860
our bond,

136
00:10:22,460 --> 00:10:23,660
shouldn't you at least

137
00:10:24,220 --> 00:10:25,620
add one more slot?

138
00:10:27,220 --> 00:10:28,580
What bond?

139
00:10:30,220 --> 00:10:31,700
You're reneging on your promise.

140
00:10:32,620 --> 00:10:34,500
I...

141
00:10:34,540 --> 00:10:36,020
I'll prove it to you.

142
00:10:36,820 --> 00:10:37,660
I...

143
00:10:39,420 --> 00:10:40,260
Here we go again.

144
00:10:49,060 --> 00:10:49,900
Let go of me.

145
00:11:12,700 --> 00:11:13,620
Xiao Jue.

146
00:11:15,500 --> 00:11:18,220
If you don't give me that extra slot,

147
00:11:19,140 --> 00:11:20,140
I'll...

148
00:11:21,420 --> 00:11:22,580
I'll...

149
00:11:24,020 --> 00:11:24,940
What will you do?

150
00:11:26,860 --> 00:11:28,060
I'll...

151
00:11:30,500 --> 00:11:31,820
I'll...

152
00:11:45,780 --> 00:11:46,820
Comfortable sleep?

153
00:11:49,140 --> 00:11:50,300
Very cozy.

154
00:12:00,260 --> 00:12:01,100
Mr. He,

155
00:12:01,340 --> 00:12:04,220
you slept soundly in Huaijin's tent.

156
00:12:04,780 --> 00:12:06,100
Truly extraordinary.

157
00:12:12,500 --> 00:12:13,340
The Commander's tent?

158
00:12:13,820 --> 00:12:14,660
Yes.

159
00:12:17,700 --> 00:12:19,340
To make space for you,

160
00:12:19,430 --> 00:12:20,700
last night,

161
00:12:20,700 --> 00:12:22,500
Huaijin squeezed into my place.

162
00:12:23,060 --> 00:12:24,820
Well? Did you remember anything?

163
00:13:02,540 --> 00:13:04,260
Seems like you did.

164
00:13:05,060 --> 00:13:06,780
Did he mention how to punish me?

165
00:13:07,500 --> 00:13:08,340
No.

166
00:13:10,020 --> 00:13:11,700
But he looked furious.

167
00:13:13,460 --> 00:13:14,300
Oh no.

168
00:13:16,700 --> 00:13:18,060
Oh no, oh no.

169
00:13:18,060 --> 00:13:18,900
Forget the battalion.

170
00:13:18,900 --> 00:13:20,100
I might not stay here anymore.

171
00:13:20,820 --> 00:13:22,060
What to do? What to do?

172
00:13:22,260 --> 00:13:23,100
Not necessarily.

173
00:13:24,420 --> 00:13:25,260
Consider this.

174
00:13:25,500 --> 00:13:27,460
You used his treasured sword

175
00:13:27,460 --> 00:13:29,100
to smash his beloved zither,

176
00:13:29,100 --> 00:13:30,140
but he didn't kill you

177
00:13:30,220 --> 00:13:31,460
and even made space for you.

178
00:13:32,340 --> 00:13:33,180
Think about it.

179
00:13:33,700 --> 00:13:35,180
Why did he treat you so kindly?

180
00:13:36,380 --> 00:13:37,620
He must've noticed

181
00:13:37,780 --> 00:13:39,820
your unique physique.

182
00:13:44,580 --> 00:13:45,500
Unique...

183
00:13:48,020 --> 00:13:49,580
Unique physique?

184
00:13:54,340 --> 00:13:55,180
(Could it be)

185
00:13:55,460 --> 00:13:57,060
(he discovered I'm a woman?)

186
00:13:57,900 --> 00:14:00,060
You're a rare prodigy.

187
00:14:00,220 --> 00:14:01,660
That's why he tolerates you.

188
00:14:04,980 --> 00:14:05,820
Am I wrong?

189
00:14:29,140 --> 00:14:29,980
Xiao Jue.

190
00:14:30,570 --> 00:14:32,040
Do you know who I am?

191
00:14:33,380 --> 00:14:35,740
I'm the top one of Yezhou Garrison,

192
00:14:38,140 --> 00:14:39,740
an outstanding candidate.

193
00:14:40,420 --> 00:14:41,540
You

194
00:14:41,540 --> 00:14:43,100
have terrible judgment!

195
00:14:44,060 --> 00:14:44,900
Commander,

196
00:14:44,900 --> 00:14:46,380
please don't be angry.

197
00:14:46,620 --> 00:14:49,260
I'll perform a sword dance for you.

198
00:14:54,020 --> 00:14:55,300
My misbehavior demands

199
00:14:56,020 --> 00:14:57,980
a proper apology to the Commander.

200
00:15:29,860 --> 00:15:30,740
Light on his feet,

201
00:15:31,580 --> 00:15:32,500
with steady breath.

202
00:15:32,740 --> 00:15:33,580
A skilled fighter.

203
00:15:36,580 --> 00:15:40,300
(Invitation)

204
00:15:45,300 --> 00:15:46,140
Summon Cheng Lisu.

205
00:15:47,060 --> 00:15:47,900
Yes.

206
00:15:54,540 --> 00:15:55,380
Commander,

207
00:15:55,740 --> 00:15:57,980
drunken words
shouldn't be taken seriously.

208
00:15:58,700 --> 00:15:59,540
Well,

209
00:15:59,820 --> 00:16:00,660
strike me ten times

210
00:16:01,140 --> 00:16:02,260
and let this matter rest.

211
00:16:06,740 --> 00:16:07,580
Commander,

212
00:16:07,820 --> 00:16:08,660
or perhaps

213
00:16:09,220 --> 00:16:10,820
I'll forfeit three years' pay

214
00:16:11,180 --> 00:16:12,540
to compensate for your zither.

215
00:16:13,420 --> 00:16:14,580
Please show mercy.

216
00:16:15,460 --> 00:16:16,300
Could you

217
00:16:17,100 --> 00:16:18,260
let me join the battalion?

218
00:16:19,780 --> 00:16:20,620
He,

219
00:16:21,060 --> 00:16:23,260
what are you muttering about alone here?

220
00:16:23,900 --> 00:16:25,380
Are you looking for extra training?

221
00:16:26,700 --> 00:16:27,820
Considering an apology.

222
00:16:28,300 --> 00:16:29,340
Considering an apology?

223
00:16:31,980 --> 00:16:32,940
Kneeling on this?

224
00:16:35,420 --> 00:16:36,860
This place is truly vast.

225
00:16:37,500 --> 00:16:38,660
Thank you so much, young man.

226
00:16:39,700 --> 00:16:40,700
If I walked alone,

227
00:16:41,540 --> 00:16:42,660
I'd likely get lost.

228
00:16:43,420 --> 00:16:44,260
(Miss He,)

229
00:16:44,540 --> 00:16:46,980
(in your next life, avoid being
born into He family.)

230
00:16:54,700 --> 00:16:55,540
It's him.

231
00:17:02,420 --> 00:17:03,260
He.

232
00:17:03,820 --> 00:17:05,060
Not picking a weapon?

233
00:17:18,660 --> 00:17:19,500
Sir,

234
00:17:19,980 --> 00:17:20,819
earlier,

235
00:17:20,819 --> 00:17:22,700
who was that person with you?

236
00:17:22,940 --> 00:17:24,619
The Yezhou Magistrate's man.

237
00:17:24,940 --> 00:17:26,700
He delivered an invitation
to our Commander.

238
00:17:27,260 --> 00:17:28,099
Thank you.

239
00:17:29,380 --> 00:17:30,700
(Yezhou Magistrate's man?)

240
00:17:31,460 --> 00:17:32,300
(His severed finger)

241
00:17:32,580 --> 00:17:33,420
(and his voice.)

242
00:17:33,900 --> 00:17:35,660
(It's the man
who hurt me at Yuhua Temple.)

243
00:17:36,420 --> 00:17:37,780
(The He family's henchman.)

244
00:17:38,660 --> 00:17:40,620
(They infiltrated Yezhou Magistrate.)

245
00:17:41,180 --> 00:17:42,180
(What are they planning?)

246
00:17:44,140 --> 00:17:47,050
Yezhou Garrison faces shortages
in military funds and provisions.

247
00:17:47,140 --> 00:17:48,820
I feel deeply concerned.

248
00:17:49,140 --> 00:17:52,060
We sincerely invite
Commander Xiao Jue of Yezhou Garrison

249
00:17:52,220 --> 00:17:53,300
for discussion.

250
00:17:53,900 --> 00:17:56,780
I also hear your nephew Cheng Lisu
is currently at Yezhou Garrison.

251
00:17:57,300 --> 00:17:59,420
Having not seen him for years,

252
00:17:59,460 --> 00:18:00,540
I feel nostalgic.

253
00:18:01,020 --> 00:18:03,380
Hoping the Commander
will bring him along.

254
00:18:03,820 --> 00:18:06,020
(Invitation)
Yezhou Magistrate, Sun Xiangfu.

255
00:18:08,540 --> 00:18:10,700
He's inviting you
for an official matter.

256
00:18:10,900 --> 00:18:11,740
Why include me?

257
00:18:12,060 --> 00:18:13,740
I have no old bonds to reminisce about.

258
00:18:16,380 --> 00:18:17,220
You don't remember?

259
00:18:22,780 --> 00:18:24,710
(Yezhou Magistrate, Sun Xiangfu)

260
00:18:27,260 --> 00:18:28,220
Sun Xiangfu!

261
00:18:30,060 --> 00:18:31,780
When he came to the capital years ago,

262
00:18:31,780 --> 00:18:33,500
his wife arranged a marriage for you.

263
00:18:34,380 --> 00:18:35,340
Oh, no.

264
00:18:35,340 --> 00:18:37,180
He'll probably lure me there first,

265
00:18:37,500 --> 00:18:38,380
then detain me,

266
00:18:38,700 --> 00:18:40,620
and send me back
to Yaojing for marriage!

267
00:18:41,180 --> 00:18:42,020
This...

268
00:18:43,140 --> 00:18:43,980
Huaijin.

269
00:18:44,900 --> 00:18:45,740
Uncle.

270
00:18:45,860 --> 00:18:47,720
You have to save me.

271
00:18:47,720 --> 00:18:50,180
You can't watch your best friend,

272
00:18:50,180 --> 00:18:51,220
your adorable nephew,

273
00:18:51,220 --> 00:18:52,340
jump into hellfire.

274
00:18:59,820 --> 00:19:00,940
Is it that terrible?

275
00:19:01,340 --> 00:19:02,260
Absolutely.

276
00:19:02,700 --> 00:19:03,780
You know full well

277
00:19:04,140 --> 00:19:06,100
Miss Song and I despise each other.

278
00:19:06,220 --> 00:19:07,540
She spends all day tinkering with

279
00:19:07,580 --> 00:19:08,540
strange concoctions.

280
00:19:09,180 --> 00:19:10,500
I'll become her lab rat,

281
00:19:10,500 --> 00:19:12,140
slowly tortured to death.

282
00:19:12,660 --> 00:19:13,500
I'd rather

283
00:19:14,020 --> 00:19:15,460
end it all now!

284
00:19:15,580 --> 00:19:16,420
Wait.

285
00:19:16,900 --> 00:19:17,740
Uncle,

286
00:19:17,740 --> 00:19:19,300
I knew you wouldn't abandon me.

287
00:19:20,180 --> 00:19:21,180
Our bond is so strong.

288
00:19:23,740 --> 00:19:25,140
W-What...?

289
00:19:27,500 --> 00:19:28,900
What are you doing?

290
00:19:34,660 --> 00:19:36,020
Yinqiu is sharp.

291
00:19:37,340 --> 00:19:38,180
I'll lend it to you.

292
00:19:39,050 --> 00:19:41,580
You're joking?

293
00:19:42,140 --> 00:19:42,980
Uncle,

294
00:19:43,580 --> 00:19:46,820
you wouldn't really
let me die, would you?

295
00:19:50,780 --> 00:19:52,220
Don't you want to end it all?

296
00:19:52,820 --> 00:19:53,660
I...

297
00:19:54,260 --> 00:19:55,720
I was just kidding.

298
00:20:06,620 --> 00:20:07,460
Mr. Cheng,

299
00:20:08,340 --> 00:20:10,380
I heard someone sent
the Commander an invitation.

300
00:20:11,060 --> 00:20:11,900
Mr. He,

301
00:20:12,020 --> 00:20:13,140
I'm going to die.

302
00:20:13,580 --> 00:20:14,420
When the time comes,

303
00:20:14,620 --> 00:20:16,100
burn lots of joss paper for me.

304
00:20:16,780 --> 00:20:18,260
Mr. Cheng, what's wrong?

305
00:20:18,860 --> 00:20:20,060
I'm going with Huaijin

306
00:20:20,100 --> 00:20:22,540
to visit the Yezhou Magistrate.

307
00:20:22,940 --> 00:20:24,300
That's a dangerous place.

308
00:20:25,020 --> 00:20:25,900
Dangerous place?

309
00:20:26,260 --> 00:20:27,540
With the Commander, why fear?

310
00:20:27,980 --> 00:20:30,140
Unless in the magistrate's mansion,

311
00:20:30,500 --> 00:20:31,420
there are people

312
00:20:31,580 --> 00:20:32,740
stronger than the Commander?

313
00:20:33,340 --> 00:20:35,420
Sun Xiangfu is more terrifying.

314
00:20:36,020 --> 00:20:37,740
His wife was my marriage matchmaker.

315
00:20:38,140 --> 00:20:38,980
This time,

316
00:20:39,220 --> 00:20:40,820
not even Xiao Jue can protect me.

317
00:20:42,740 --> 00:20:45,140
So the Commander is visiting Yezhou

318
00:20:45,140 --> 00:20:46,580
to discuss your marriage?

319
00:20:46,740 --> 00:20:47,580
No.

320
00:20:47,700 --> 00:20:49,260
He is going for an official matter.

321
00:20:49,420 --> 00:20:51,780
Only I must go through this.

322
00:20:52,500 --> 00:20:54,310
Official matter?

323
00:20:54,310 --> 00:20:55,300
What is that?

324
00:20:55,300 --> 00:20:58,060
The Yezhou Magistrate wants
the Commander's personal presence?

325
00:20:58,140 --> 00:20:59,300
He's got some nerve.

326
00:21:00,060 --> 00:21:00,900
No.

327
00:21:00,980 --> 00:21:02,660
Huaijin is going
for provisions and funds.

328
00:21:03,060 --> 00:21:03,900
I'm just...

329
00:21:04,200 --> 00:21:05,180
Hold on, Mr. He.

330
00:21:05,580 --> 00:21:06,980
Why do you keep mentioning Huaijin?

331
00:21:07,380 --> 00:21:09,460
I'm the one in hot water, not him.

332
00:21:11,460 --> 00:21:12,300
Mr. Cheng,

333
00:21:12,700 --> 00:21:14,620
I just thought he'd be capable enough.

334
00:21:14,940 --> 00:21:16,260
If you can't rely on him,

335
00:21:17,140 --> 00:21:18,420
let me help brainstorm ideas.

336
00:21:19,780 --> 00:21:20,620
Come on, let's go.

337
00:21:21,300 --> 00:21:22,380
Let me think.

338
00:21:23,420 --> 00:21:24,260
Commander,

339
00:21:24,780 --> 00:21:25,660
Sun Xiangfu has been

340
00:21:26,100 --> 00:21:27,980
dodging the funds and provisions issue,

341
00:21:28,260 --> 00:21:29,510
but at this critical moment,

342
00:21:29,510 --> 00:21:30,540
he suddenly invites you.

343
00:21:30,660 --> 00:21:31,700
It must be a trap.

344
00:21:31,780 --> 00:21:33,660
This is clearly an ambush banquet.

345
00:21:34,220 --> 00:21:35,060
Should we decline?

346
00:21:35,980 --> 00:21:36,820
If I don't go,

347
00:21:37,260 --> 00:21:38,500
they won't give up.

348
00:21:39,140 --> 00:21:40,620
A stab in the back is hard to dodge.

349
00:21:41,460 --> 00:21:42,580
We should strike first.

350
00:21:43,220 --> 00:21:44,060
Moreover,

351
00:21:44,540 --> 00:21:47,140
doesn't Sun Xiangfu
still owe us for the provisions?

352
00:21:47,340 --> 00:21:48,180
Commander.

353
00:21:48,180 --> 00:21:49,300
I've just received news.

354
00:21:49,660 --> 00:21:51,900
The Inspector
of the Ministry of War, Chu Zhao,

355
00:21:51,900 --> 00:21:52,820
is coming to Yezhou.

356
00:21:53,260 --> 00:21:54,620
I think you know this man.

357
00:21:54,740 --> 00:21:57,580
Top scholar in 19th Year of Qingyuan,
Xu Jingfu's prized disciple.

358
00:21:58,260 --> 00:22:00,500
He's been serving
Xu Jingfu all these years.

359
00:22:01,380 --> 00:22:02,220
I find he just

360
00:22:02,700 --> 00:22:03,900
returned from Que City.

361
00:22:08,300 --> 00:22:09,140
Continue.

362
00:22:09,700 --> 00:22:10,540
The Que City battle

363
00:22:10,620 --> 00:22:11,460
hurt your reputation.

364
00:22:11,780 --> 00:22:13,140
It's unclear if he's involved.

365
00:22:13,420 --> 00:22:14,260
Now in Yezhou,

366
00:22:14,700 --> 00:22:16,460
his intentions here remain unknown.

367
00:22:17,140 --> 00:22:18,460
I've dealt with Chu Zhao before.

368
00:22:19,260 --> 00:22:21,460
He suffered mistreatment
in his family initially

369
00:22:21,820 --> 00:22:22,860
until he earned his title,

370
00:22:23,740 --> 00:22:25,460
and then his family
changed their attitude.

371
00:22:26,100 --> 00:22:28,020
Now, he serves under Xu Jingfu.

372
00:22:28,180 --> 00:22:31,140
Undoubtedly, he is using
Xu Jingfu's influence for advancement.

373
00:22:31,700 --> 00:22:33,060
Regardless of his true motives,

374
00:22:33,820 --> 00:22:36,220
he ultimately works for Xu Jingfu.

375
00:22:37,100 --> 00:22:37,940
What a coincidence.

376
00:22:38,860 --> 00:22:39,980
Returning from Que City.

377
00:22:41,180 --> 00:22:43,140
Those rumors must stem from him.

378
00:22:43,660 --> 00:22:44,820
During this Yezhou mission,

379
00:22:45,700 --> 00:22:46,820
stay vigilant against him.

380
00:22:46,980 --> 00:22:47,820
Yes.

381
00:22:47,860 --> 00:22:48,700
Commander.

382
00:22:48,860 --> 00:22:50,060
This mission is dangerous.

383
00:22:50,420 --> 00:22:51,660
Mr. Cheng can't fight.

384
00:22:52,060 --> 00:22:52,900
Taking him along

385
00:22:53,100 --> 00:22:54,340
could be problematic.

386
00:22:54,940 --> 00:22:56,060
Cheng Lisu isn't going.

387
00:22:56,380 --> 00:22:57,340
He Yan will go.

388
00:23:04,660 --> 00:23:05,500
What's wrong?

389
00:23:06,300 --> 00:23:07,140
No problem.

390
00:23:07,660 --> 00:23:09,700
Commander, don't you doubt
He Yan's identity?

391
00:23:10,100 --> 00:23:11,700
Why bring him along then?

392
00:23:14,300 --> 00:23:16,460
Leaving him here worries me.

393
00:23:16,940 --> 00:23:18,300
Since he's so eager to go,

394
00:23:19,140 --> 00:23:19,980
let him join me.

395
00:23:20,780 --> 00:23:22,020
He boasts of his skills.

396
00:23:22,660 --> 00:23:23,780
This banquet will test

397
00:23:24,660 --> 00:23:26,220
whether his claims hold true.

398
00:23:34,780 --> 00:23:36,140
(Sun Xiangfu has been withholding)

399
00:23:36,220 --> 00:23:37,740
(the military provisions and funds,)

400
00:23:38,740 --> 00:23:41,420
(but now suddenly invites
Xiao Jue to negotiate.)

401
00:23:42,540 --> 00:23:44,100
(He Rufei and Sun Xiangfu)

402
00:23:44,780 --> 00:23:46,020
(must be plotting something.)

403
00:23:46,740 --> 00:23:47,580
(Their target)

404
00:23:47,900 --> 00:23:48,940
(is Yezhou Garrison,)

405
00:23:49,780 --> 00:23:51,020
(perhaps even Xiao Jue.)

406
00:23:53,420 --> 00:23:54,420
(This trip to Yezhou,)

407
00:23:55,100 --> 00:23:56,340
(whether for the garrison,)

408
00:23:56,620 --> 00:23:57,460
(Xiao Jue,)

409
00:23:57,740 --> 00:23:58,700
(or me,)

410
00:23:59,820 --> 00:24:02,140
(I must uncover the truth.)

411
00:24:22,500 --> 00:24:23,340
Commander.

412
00:24:24,180 --> 00:24:25,020
You seem distracted.

413
00:24:25,740 --> 00:24:26,580
What troubles you?

414
00:24:27,460 --> 00:24:28,300
Commander,

415
00:24:28,540 --> 00:24:29,940
I drank too much last night.

416
00:24:30,100 --> 00:24:30,980
Sorry

417
00:24:31,500 --> 00:24:32,340
for offending you.

418
00:24:32,540 --> 00:24:34,620
But must you stare at me like this?

419
00:24:34,940 --> 00:24:37,140
I've already thought of
a way to redeem myself.

420
00:24:37,900 --> 00:24:39,900
So you take Cheng Lisu's place
and go to Yezhou

421
00:24:40,260 --> 00:24:41,180
just to atone?

422
00:24:42,660 --> 00:24:43,820
Not entirely.

423
00:24:44,260 --> 00:24:45,500
Aside from easing your burdens,

424
00:24:46,060 --> 00:24:47,060
it's for my own sake.

425
00:24:47,860 --> 00:24:48,700
For yourself?

426
00:24:51,260 --> 00:24:53,420
I want to join the battalion
to make achievements.

427
00:24:53,740 --> 00:24:54,700
If this trip

428
00:24:54,740 --> 00:24:56,460
can make you change your opinion of me,

429
00:24:56,780 --> 00:24:57,620
then next time,

430
00:24:57,820 --> 00:24:58,980
the slot for the battalion

431
00:24:59,180 --> 00:25:00,020
will be mine.

432
00:25:00,380 --> 00:25:01,780
Such a golden opportunity.

433
00:25:01,940 --> 00:25:03,100
Of course I'll seize it.

434
00:25:08,820 --> 00:25:09,660
Good.

435
00:25:10,300 --> 00:25:11,380
Let's see

436
00:25:12,020 --> 00:25:13,460
how you'll change my opinion.

437
00:25:39,580 --> 00:25:40,420
Commander.

438
00:25:40,420 --> 00:25:41,260
Mr. Cheng.

439
00:25:41,380 --> 00:25:42,220
Mr. Feinu.

440
00:25:42,540 --> 00:25:43,380
Morning.

441
00:25:43,860 --> 00:25:44,700
Morning.

442
00:25:49,980 --> 00:25:51,180
I am Cheng Lisu

443
00:25:51,500 --> 00:25:52,620
from the capital.

444
00:25:53,020 --> 00:25:54,780
I love mushroom and chicken stew,

445
00:25:54,860 --> 00:25:55,900
hate congee,

446
00:25:56,260 --> 00:25:58,180
avoid peanuts
and love cleanliness the most.

447
00:25:58,340 --> 00:26:00,260
I burn incense and bathe daily.

448
00:26:00,780 --> 00:26:01,620
Well done. Well done.

449
00:26:01,740 --> 00:26:02,820
You've memorized that well.

450
00:26:04,060 --> 00:26:06,100
As the saying goes,
clothes make the man.

451
00:26:08,500 --> 00:26:09,340
This looks better.

452
00:26:13,700 --> 00:26:14,540
Mr. He,

453
00:26:14,540 --> 00:26:15,780
your demeanor today

454
00:26:15,980 --> 00:26:16,900
almost rivals mine.

455
00:26:17,460 --> 00:26:18,540
You flatter me.

456
00:26:20,060 --> 00:26:21,660
Commander, what do you think?

457
00:26:21,660 --> 00:26:22,700
Do I look

458
00:26:22,900 --> 00:26:25,700
charming and dashing?

459
00:26:26,420 --> 00:26:27,260
You're even

460
00:26:29,340 --> 00:26:30,580
shorter than Cheng Lisu.

461
00:26:33,340 --> 00:26:34,180
Who says that?

462
00:26:34,620 --> 00:26:35,460
About my height.

463
00:26:36,260 --> 00:26:37,100
When are you leaving?

464
00:26:45,860 --> 00:26:46,700
Go away.

465
00:26:53,050 --> 00:26:57,540
(Yezhou City)

466
00:27:02,540 --> 00:27:03,380
Young Master.

467
00:27:03,620 --> 00:27:05,620
Ding Yi has made contact
with Sun Xiangfu.

468
00:27:06,180 --> 00:27:08,380
The invitation for Xiao Jue
to come to Yezhou City

469
00:27:08,740 --> 00:27:10,500
must now be in his hands.

470
00:27:10,820 --> 00:27:11,660
Good.

471
00:27:12,380 --> 00:27:13,220
Found anything

472
00:27:13,500 --> 00:27:14,340
about the Sun family?

473
00:27:14,740 --> 00:27:15,900
As you instructed,

474
00:27:16,060 --> 00:27:18,100
we targeted Sun Xiangfu's useless son.

475
00:27:18,780 --> 00:27:19,700
Fruitful results.

476
00:27:20,100 --> 00:27:21,700
Sun Ling is a lecherous man,

477
00:27:21,900 --> 00:27:22,980
abusing his father's power

478
00:27:23,260 --> 00:27:25,420
to tyrannize Yezhou's citizens
and harass women.

479
00:27:25,660 --> 00:27:27,740
The people are afraid
to speak their anger openly.

480
00:27:28,060 --> 00:27:29,780
Sun Xiangfu is cautious
and stays in line,

481
00:27:30,620 --> 00:27:31,460
but he is responsible

482
00:27:31,860 --> 00:27:32,700
for his son.

483
00:27:33,220 --> 00:27:34,940
His son will surely drag him down.

484
00:27:35,740 --> 00:27:36,580
Young Master.

485
00:27:36,620 --> 00:27:37,460
In that case,

486
00:27:37,700 --> 00:27:39,540
shouldn't we head
to the Sun residence now?

487
00:27:39,820 --> 00:27:41,260
The stage is set,

488
00:27:41,660 --> 00:27:43,540
and the actors will soon arrive.

489
00:27:44,380 --> 00:27:45,820
We'll move once they're here.

490
00:27:46,740 --> 00:27:47,660
Missing this chance

491
00:27:48,340 --> 00:27:49,340
would be a shame.

492
00:28:06,700 --> 00:28:07,540
Gentlemen,

493
00:28:07,540 --> 00:28:08,700
please come inside.

494
00:28:13,980 --> 00:28:14,820
This way.

495
00:28:17,140 --> 00:28:17,980
Sir,

496
00:28:17,980 --> 00:28:18,820
please.

497
00:28:22,300 --> 00:28:27,210
(Guests Filling the Halls)

498
00:28:28,900 --> 00:28:29,740
Commander.

499
00:28:33,300 --> 00:28:34,140
Uncle.

500
00:28:34,140 --> 00:28:35,540
Why not stay at the Sun residence?

501
00:28:36,140 --> 00:28:36,980
No rush.

502
00:28:40,220 --> 00:28:42,020
How many rooms would you like?

503
00:28:42,420 --> 00:28:43,260
Three.

504
00:28:43,460 --> 00:28:44,300
Two.

505
00:28:47,100 --> 00:28:48,100
We two share a room.

506
00:28:48,900 --> 00:28:50,300
Why should I share a room with you?

507
00:28:50,580 --> 00:28:51,420
Because...

508
00:28:53,500 --> 00:28:55,980
I'm your nephew.

509
00:28:55,980 --> 00:28:58,100
You won't even pay for another room?

510
00:28:59,700 --> 00:29:00,540
Three rooms.

511
00:29:00,540 --> 00:29:01,380
Alright.

512
00:29:02,940 --> 00:29:03,780
You...

513
00:29:03,860 --> 00:29:05,220
Don't leave your room tonight.

514
00:29:09,060 --> 00:29:09,900
Waiter.

515
00:29:09,900 --> 00:29:10,740
Coming.

516
00:29:11,860 --> 00:29:14,260
Do you serve
mushroom and chicken stew here?

517
00:29:14,300 --> 00:29:15,140
Yes.

518
00:29:15,500 --> 00:29:16,340
Bring us a portion.

519
00:29:16,340 --> 00:29:17,980
Uncle, you know well

520
00:29:18,020 --> 00:29:20,380
how much I adore
mushroom and chicken stew.

521
00:29:22,540 --> 00:29:23,660
Mushroom and chicken stew,

522
00:29:24,060 --> 00:29:25,060
Eight-Treasure Duck,

523
00:29:25,300 --> 00:29:26,500
vegetables, soup,

524
00:29:26,740 --> 00:29:27,580
and six steamed buns.

525
00:29:28,300 --> 00:29:29,140
Okay.

526
00:29:29,940 --> 00:29:31,460
(Just having one more room)

527
00:29:31,500 --> 00:29:32,620
(and ordering one dish)

528
00:29:33,100 --> 00:29:34,980
(deserves those judgmental looks?)

529
00:29:35,340 --> 00:29:36,660
(So stingy.)

530
00:29:37,940 --> 00:29:38,780
Wait.

531
00:29:39,740 --> 00:29:40,660
I'll have

532
00:29:41,020 --> 00:29:43,060
spicy tripe strips, sesame rolls,

533
00:29:43,060 --> 00:29:45,540
shredded chicken with cucumber,
five-flavored steamed gluten,

534
00:29:45,540 --> 00:29:46,540
aromatic young pigeon,

535
00:29:46,540 --> 00:29:48,420
and also that

536
00:29:49,100 --> 00:29:50,180
mung bean dough noodles.

537
00:29:50,180 --> 00:29:51,780
Yes, all of them.

538
00:29:51,780 --> 00:29:53,180
- Okay.
- Can you finish all this?

539
00:29:57,700 --> 00:29:58,540
Uncle,

540
00:29:59,060 --> 00:30:00,580
you wouldn't let your nephew

541
00:30:00,780 --> 00:30:01,940
go hungry, would you?

542
00:30:06,740 --> 00:30:07,740
Serve what he ordered.

543
00:30:08,220 --> 00:30:09,060
Alright.

544
00:30:27,460 --> 00:30:28,300
Enjoy your meal.

545
00:30:29,780 --> 00:30:31,210
Since these are your favorite food,

546
00:30:31,700 --> 00:30:33,300
I naturally let you eat them.

547
00:30:33,980 --> 00:30:35,140
But I taught you this.

548
00:30:35,580 --> 00:30:36,540
Save and thrive,

549
00:30:36,980 --> 00:30:37,940
waste and perish.

550
00:30:38,980 --> 00:30:39,940
Don't waste anything.

551
00:30:45,460 --> 00:30:46,980
(I've really overdone it now.)

552
00:31:12,500 --> 00:31:14,820
I'm stuffed!

553
00:31:15,820 --> 00:31:17,830
Now that I'm full, I'm getting drowsy.

554
00:31:17,830 --> 00:31:20,220
This bed is amazingly comfortable!

555
00:31:22,420 --> 00:31:25,500
I'll definitely sleep well.

556
00:31:26,420 --> 00:31:28,220
He eats well and sleeps soundly.

557
00:31:28,780 --> 00:31:31,260
If you're still energetic,
play chess with me.

558
00:32:03,820 --> 00:32:04,660
Commander,

559
00:32:04,740 --> 00:32:05,740
really playing chess?

560
00:32:06,380 --> 00:32:07,220
But I...

561
00:32:12,940 --> 00:32:14,500
Yezhou City has unexpected people.

562
00:32:15,180 --> 00:32:16,220
This is getting exciting.

563
00:32:16,740 --> 00:32:18,100
Investigate the Sun family again.

564
00:32:18,580 --> 00:32:20,420
Find their recent tax records.

565
00:32:20,900 --> 00:32:22,380
Let's see how Sun Xiangfu

566
00:32:23,060 --> 00:32:24,780
claims military provisions are lacking

567
00:32:24,980 --> 00:32:26,220
and he can't allocate rations.

568
00:32:26,980 --> 00:32:27,820
Yes.

569
00:32:28,740 --> 00:32:29,580
Commander,

570
00:32:29,940 --> 00:32:30,780
what about He Yan?

571
00:32:31,180 --> 00:32:32,300
I'll keep watch personally.

572
00:33:03,710 --> 00:33:05,860
♪Light shines upon my heart♪

573
00:33:05,970 --> 00:33:09,890
♪Unveiling scars,
I choose to swim upstream♪

574
00:33:10,060 --> 00:33:12,010
♪The resonance of courage
rings loud and clear♪

575
00:33:12,100 --> 00:33:17,030
♪It's the boldness
that defines existence♪

576
00:33:29,130 --> 00:33:30,530
♪I've seen the mountains♪

577
00:33:30,730 --> 00:33:32,150
♪And trodden through ice♪

578
00:33:32,420 --> 00:33:35,230
♪Day after day, I venture alone♪

579
00:33:35,540 --> 00:33:36,930
♪Destiny is my creed♪

580
00:33:36,990 --> 00:33:38,390
♪Ideals surge beneath the surface♪

581
